c: 57
v: 9
t: "hw aladhi yunazil ealaa eabdah muhamad salaa allah ealayh wasalam ayat mufasalat wadhat min alqran; liyukhrijakum bidhulik min zulmat alkufr 'iilaa nur al'iyman, 'iina allah bikum fi 'iikhrajikum min alzulumat 'iilaa alnuwr liarhmkm rahmat wasieat fi eajlkm wajlkm, fyjazykm 'ahsan aljza'"